The '''energy collector core''' was a structure used by the [[InterGalactic Banking Clan/Legends|InterGalactic Banking Clan]] to power the [[Droid/Legends|droid]] [[Factory/Legends|factories]] stationed on [[Mygeeto/Legends|Mygeeto]]. The core was powered by an [[energy crystal]].

During the [[Battle of Mygeeto]] of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], the [[501st Legion/Legends|501st Legion]] destroyed the core and collected a sample of its crystal, which would later power the [[Superlaser/Legends|superlaser]] of the [[Hammertong/Legends|Hammertong]] project.

